snippet.title: Good Dog, Bad Dog - Gameplay Trailer | PS4, PS VR
snippet.description:
Good Dog, Bad Dog - Be the dog you want to be! 

Coming soon to PlayStation®4 and PlayStation®VR!

See and experience the world through the eyes of a dog. Choose your dog and your owner and explore the neighborhood. Play fetch, give your paw, get petted, eat snacks to be a Good Dog, or bite, bark, and barf on the residents of your neighborhood to be a Bad Dog! Dig up toys or snacks around the environment while avoiding the dog catcher when you are off the leash!
